What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Tea Packaging Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Tea Packaging Market

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the tea packaging market will project a CAGR of 5.50% for the forecast period of 2021-2028. Rising focus on the packaging product innovations by the manufacturers, growth and expansion of packaging industry especially in the developing economies and increased personal disposable income are the factors driving the growth of tea packaging market. Therefore, the market value, which was USD 8,100 million in 2020, will rocket up to USD 12,430.96 million by 2028.

Tea is one of the most widely consumed non-alcoholic beverages. Derived from Camellia Sinensis plant, tea is an aromatic beverage and is available in a wide range of varieties such as black tea, green tea, oolong tea, herbal tea and so on. And since, tea is a beverage, it requires a specific packaging solution to prevent spilling and protect it from getting contaminated by the external environment.

Rising demand for sustainable packaging solutions is driving the growth in the market value. Growing demand for aromatic beverages and growth and expansion of the food and beverages industry especially in the developing economies will further induce growth in the market value. Rising proliferation of e-commerce industry especially in the developing economies, growing demand for packaged products from the retailers, increasing westernization, modernization, urbanization, ever-rising global population, growing awareness about the benefits of herbal tea, rising health consciousness and increasing personal disposable income are some other indirect factors that will also promote the market growth rate.

However, fluctuations in the prices of packaging materials will create hindrances for the market growth rate. Rising costs of innovative packaging solutions will further dampen the market growth rate. Also, infrastructural challenges in developing countries will hamper the market growth rate.

